1276
00:40:34,639 --> 00:40:36,609
- What's that?
- We aren't eating for free.

1277
00:40:36,709 --> 00:40:38,539
- All right, everyone.
- Do we spin that?

1278
00:40:38,539 --> 00:40:40,749
- Aren't you getting hungry?
- Of course.

1279
00:40:40,749 --> 00:40:42,649
Stop asking, and let's move on.

1280
00:40:42,649 --> 00:40:44,649
We don't have time, so don't talk to us.

1281
00:40:46,279 --> 00:40:49,019
This is where you can experience the fresh taste of the East Sea.

1282
00:40:49,019 --> 00:40:50,359
(Where you can experience the East Sea of Uljin)

1283
00:40:50,759 --> 00:40:53,859
