1288
00:41:04,839 --> 00:41:06,169
Braised codfish head sounds delicious.

1289
00:41:06,299 --> 00:41:07,869
There's a lot of meat in the cheeks.

1290
00:41:08,439 --> 00:41:10,269
Do you see the spinning wheel?

1291
00:41:10,269 --> 00:41:11,639
- Yes.
- Please take off...

1292
