1298
00:41:26,589 --> 00:41:27,589
(Braised codfish head, 10 minutes)

1299
00:41:27,589 --> 00:41:28,759
Braised codfish head takes ten minutes.

1300
00:41:28,759 --> 00:41:29,829
That's a long time.

1301
00:41:30,129 --> 00:41:33,059
(Codfish head soup, 5 minutes)

1302
00:41:33,499 --> 00:41:34,629
(Chopped small octopus, 5 minutes)

1303
00:41:34,629 --> 00:41:35,729
(Stir-fried live small octopus, 5 minutes)

1304
00:41:35,929 --> 00:41:37,699
How does it take one minute to cook octopus soup?

1305
00:41:37,769 --> 00:41:40,269
Don't you just cook it with octopus in it?

1306
00:41:40,539 --> 00:41:42,569
So you're willing to give us food for free.

1307
00:41:42,769 --> 00:41:43,779
Of course.

1308
00:41:43,779 --> 00:41:45,479
Isn't ten minutes okay?

1309
00:41:45,479 --> 00:41:47,609
- It's okay.
- Ten minutes is okay, right?

1310
00:41:48,049 --> 00:41:51,249
