1311
00:41:51,849 --> 00:41:54,319
- There's also cup ramyeon.
- Cup ramyeon would be...

1312
00:41:54,319 --> 00:41:55,749
- the most convenient for us.
- It would reduce time.

1313
00:41:56,089 --> 00:41:59,319
I don't know what owner's choice is.

1314
00:41:59,619 --> 00:42:03,559
Everyone, you may eat whatever you want.

1315
00:42:04,059 --> 00:42:07,229
However, you can only eat the item you get on the spinning wheel.

1316
00:42:07,229 --> 00:42:10,129
Once you finish the entire dish,

1317
00:42:10,129 --> 00:42:11,539
