1318
00:42:11,539 --> 00:42:12,699
- We can eat more?
- Yes.

1319
00:42:12,699 --> 00:42:14,569
This might not be good for us.

1320
00:42:14,569 --> 00:42:15,769
- Right.
- We would spend more time.

1321
00:42:15,769 --> 00:42:17,039
- If we...
- We can't eat all at once.

1322
00:42:17,039 --> 00:42:18,939
If we get the octopus soup,

1323
00:42:18,939 --> 00:42:20,709
