1330
00:42:34,029 --> 00:42:36,859
We must think about the future. Even if we suffer a little now...

1331
00:42:36,859 --> 00:42:39,729
Think about walking 10km to 20km later.

1332
00:42:39,729 --> 00:42:43,029
