1333
00:42:43,029 --> 00:42:45,369
It takes nine hours from Pohang to Gyeongju on foot.

1334
00:42:45,369 --> 00:42:46,399
Yes, don't forget that.

1335
00:42:46,399 --> 00:42:47,439
If we get red bean bingsu,

1336
00:42:47,439 --> 00:42:48,939
