1339
00:42:54,479 --> 00:42:58,249
We should still try the braised codfish head.

1340
00:42:58,249 --> 00:42:59,549
You little brats.

1341
00:42:59,549 --> 00:43:01,919
Don't ignore the present while preparing for the future.

1342
00:43:01,919 --> 00:43:02,919
(The present is also important.)

1343
00:43:02,919 --> 00:43:03,919
Eating braised codfish head is the present.

1344
00:43:03,919 --> 00:43:05,119
A hungry Socrates is better off...

1345
00:43:05,119 --> 00:43:06,959
than a stuffed pig.

1346
00:43:07,119 --> 00:43:08,929
A stuffed pig would be so happy.

1347
00:43:09,529 --> 00:43:10,599
It'd be easy to fall asleep.

1348
00:43:10,659 --> 00:43:12,759
Don't you know how good it feels to sleep after a blood sugar spike?

1349
00:43:14,299 --> 00:43:15,829
Let's get one braised codfish head.

1350
00:43:16,199 --> 00:43:18,239
I agree. We must try that.

1351
00:43:18,239 --> 00:43:19,399
- We need to try it.
- Yes.

1352
00:43:19,399 --> 00:43:21,169
- We're gourmands.
- We must try braised codfish head.

1353
00:43:21,369 --> 00:43:23,709
We're wasting time right now.

1354
00:43:23,709 --> 00:43:24,809
