- Just spin it.

1356
00:43:27,139 --> 00:43:28,779
- The youngest should spin it.
- We won't resent you.

1357
00:43:28,779 --> 00:43:30,349
No, we won't.

1358
00:43:30,349 --> 00:43:31,819
- Just do it.
- We won't resent you.

1359
00:43:31,819 --> 00:43:34,219
- You won't resent me, right?
- Spin it.

1360
00:43:34,219 --> 00:43:35,949
(We won't resent you. Just spin it!)

1361
00:43:35,949 --> 00:43:37,489
Here I go.

1362
00:43:37,689 --> 00:43:38,789
Let's go.

1363
00:43:39,059 --> 00:43:40,419
- What will it be?
- Braised codfish head.

1364
00:43:41,129 --> 00:43:42,889
- Let's get it in one go.
- Braised codfish head.

1365
00:43:43,059 --> 00:43:44,399
- Please.
- Braised codfish head.

1366
00:43:44,429 --> 00:43:46,229
- Let's get braised codfish head.
- Please.

1367
00:43:46,999 --> 00:43:48,029
Let's get braised codfish head.

1368
00:43:48,069 --> 00:43:49,599
- Braised codfish head.
- Let's get braised codfish head.

1369
00:43:49,599 --> 00:43:51,269
(They're united right now.)

1370
00:43:51,269 --> 00:43:53,099
- Braised codfish head.
- What is it?

1371
00:43:53,369 --> 00:43:55,469
(They draw braised codfish head successfully.)

1372
00:43:55,469 --> 00:43:56,739
- It's braised codfish head.
- It's braised codfish head.

1373
00:43:56,739 --> 00:43:57,739
(We're proud of you, Ki Taek.)

1374
00:43:57,739 --> 00:43:59,709
- That's amazing.
- We got braised codfish head.

1375
00:43:59,709 --> 00:44:01,879
(Ki Taek united Team Eat and Team Go.)

1376
00:44:02,179 --> 00:44:03,379
Braised codfish head.

1377
00:44:03,479 --> 00:44:05,549
We'll have to eat braised codfish head.

1378
00:44:05,749 --> 00:44:07,689
That was amazing. Nice.

1379
00:44:08,549 --> 00:44:10,049
Good job, Ki Taek.

1380
00:44:10,819 --> 00:44:14,659
At 12:40pm, your braised codfish head is getting prepared.

1381
00:44:14,659 --> 00:44:16,659
After eating braised codfish head,

1382
00:44:16,659 --> 00:44:18,899
- We should go.
- how about an octopus soup?

1383
00:44:19,029 --> 00:44:21,299
- To finish clean.
- Se Yoon, we can't do that.

1384
00:44:21,299 --> 00:44:22,629
- You sloppy fatty.
- You punk.

1385
00:44:22,629 --> 00:44:25,239
If we pick another dish,

1386
00:44:25,239 --> 00:44:26,899
