- Right.

1387
00:44:26,899 --> 00:44:28,169
- That would be ridiculous.
- That's risky.

1388
00:44:28,169 --> 00:44:30,269
- It also takes ten minutes to cook.
- It's risky.

1389
00:44:30,269 --> 00:44:31,979
It's dangerous. It takes too much time.

1390
00:44:32,179 --> 00:44:33,339
Chopped small octopus sounds...

1391
00:44:33,339 --> 00:44:34,879
