1408
00:45:06,539 --> 00:45:08,749
What if he makes it omakase?

1409
00:45:08,749 --> 00:45:10,649
He might go to catch a codfish.

1410
00:45:10,649 --> 00:45:12,449
Right, he might go to catch one.

1411
00:45:12,479 --> 00:45:13,919
No, we'd be in big trouble.

1412
00:45:13,989 --> 00:45:16,649
Shouldn't they serve us side dishes to save us time?

1413
00:45:16,649 --> 00:45:17,759
Right.

1414
00:45:17,759 --> 00:45:19,389
- Hasn't it been over ten minutes?
- I know.

1415
00:45:19,389 --> 00:45:21,089
- It's been seven minutes.
- Okay.

1416
00:45:21,089 --> 00:45:22,629
You have to keep your promise. We're watching.

1417
00:45:22,629 --> 00:45:24,499
I'm looking at my watch.

1418
00:45:24,999 --> 00:45:26,459
It has to be served within ten minutes.

1419
00:45:26,729 --> 00:45:28,229
- Okay.
- We have two minutes left.

1420
00:45:28,229 --> 00:45:29,229
All right.

1421
00:45:29,229 --> 00:45:30,399
