1424
00:45:32,939 --> 00:45:34,869
- All right, ten...
- You should be on time.

1425
00:45:34,869 --> 00:45:36,439
- It's here.
- There it is.

1426
00:45:36,439 --> 00:45:37,679
- The food is here.
- It's here.

1427
00:45:37,679 --> 00:45:38,739
It's here.

1428
00:45:38,739 --> 00:45:40,779
It's really served within ten minutes.

1429
00:45:40,779 --> 00:45:43,409
Hold on, that's not right.

1430
00:45:43,409 --> 00:45:44,979
- What?
- Oh, come on.

1431
00:45:44,979 --> 00:45:46,119
We'd finish it in seconds.

1432
00:45:46,719 --> 00:45:48,749
