- I made a mistake.

1456
00:46:35,429 --> 00:46:36,529
Let me serve you rice.

1457
00:46:36,529 --> 00:46:37,699
I'll give you bean sprouts.

1458
00:46:37,699 --> 00:46:39,369
Gulp down the food and rotate.

1459
00:46:39,369 --> 00:46:40,709
Who wants more?

1460
00:46:40,839 --> 00:46:42,139
(He starts eating.)

1461
00:46:42,139 --> 00:46:43,269
It's good.

1462
00:46:44,339 --> 00:46:45,339
