1463
00:46:45,339 --> 00:46:47,079
(side by side.)

1464
00:46:47,179 --> 00:46:48,549
- The seasoning is good, isn't it?
- Who wants more rice?

1465
00:46:48,879 --> 00:46:50,149
I must admit that it's good.

1466
00:46:50,149 --> 00:46:51,219
(Based on the color, it can't be bad.)

1467
00:46:51,219 --> 00:46:54,189
The food is still good.

1468
00:46:54,189 --> 00:46:55,249
My, it's good.

1469
00:46:55,249 --> 00:46:57,249
(It's a small portion, but it tastes good.)

1470
00:46:57,919 --> 00:46:59,189
(One bite)

1471
00:46:59,459 --> 00:47:01,329
(Two bites)

1472
00:47:01,659 --> 00:47:02,659
(It's gone in just three bites.)

1473
00:47:02,659 --> 00:47:03,859
- Shall we spin it now?
- Yes, let's do that.

1474
00:47:04,299 --> 00:47:05,429
No, we have to go now.

1475
00:47:05,599 --> 00:47:07,099
We should go. We can't spin it again.

1476
00:47:07,529 --> 00:47:09,329
We need to get some more food, right?

1477
00:47:09,329 --> 00:47:10,569
No, we have to go.

1478
00:47:11,569 --> 00:47:13,139
- Will you eat some more?
- Yes.

1479
00:47:13,599 --> 00:47:15,239
(I only tried a bit.)

1480
00:47:15,239 --> 00:47:16,309
Yes, I'll eat some more.

1481
00:47:16,639 --> 00:47:18,579
Yong Jin, spin it.

1482
00:47:19,179 --> 00:47:20,439
- Go on. Why?
- Hold on.

1483
00:47:20,439 --> 00:47:21,749
- Wait until everyone is finished.
- We're all finished.

1484
00:47:22,409 --> 00:47:25,719
