(Stir-fried live small octopus with rice, cooking time: 5 minutes)

1502
00:47:55,549 --> 00:47:57,549
- Small octopus.
- Stir-fried small octopus. Okay.

1503
00:47:57,549 --> 00:47:58,879
- It only takes five minutes.
- Stir-fried live small octopus.

1504
00:47:58,879 --> 00:48:00,719
- Five-minute cooking time is nice.
- Five minutes? That's great.

1505
00:48:00,719 --> 00:48:02,619
- Start timing.
- Stir-fried live small octopus.

1506
00:48:02,619 --> 00:48:04,659
It's exactly 12:53:25pm. Let's go.

1507
00:48:04,659 --> 00:48:05,989
We almost got octopus soup.

1508
00:48:05,989 --> 00:48:07,159
What a shame.

1509
00:48:07,689 --> 00:48:08,789
You have five minutes.

1510
00:48:08,789 --> 00:48:10,429
- Gosh. Cup ramyeon...
- It's not bad at all.

1511
00:48:10,689 --> 00:48:12,229
That won't fill me up.

1512
00:48:12,229 --> 00:48:13,529
- That's true.
